        return (p2[1] - p1[1]) ** 2 - (p2[0] - p1[0]) ** 2
    f1 = (x1, y1)

        dist_f2.append(Dist(p, f2))
        points.append((Dist(p, f1), dist_f2[-1]))
    points.sort()
    dist_f2.sort()
    ans = min(max(dist_f2), points[-1][0])

        r_need = 0
        for j in range(i + 1, n):
            if points[j][1] > r_need:
                r_need = points[j][1]
        ind = bisect_left(dist_f2, r_need)
        r2 = dist_f2[ind]

    return ans
